  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0874637cabf445b44aa6cb3553862f49, type: 3}
  m_Name: Mata_9
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::PenyakitData
  tagBahagian: Mata
  namaPenyakit: Glaucoma
  namaPenyakitEN: Glaucoma
  tahapRisiko: Tahap 3
  tahapRisikoEN: Level 3
  gambar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ce46ee2c520ce25439a314e7e93ff2d9, type: 3}
  isGraphic: 0
  punca: Peningkatan tekanan dalam mata akibat pengumpulan bendalir, selalunya diwarisi.
    Cecair jernih yang mengisi ruang di bahagian depan (Anterior Chamber)
  simptom: Mata kelihatan keruh/kebiruan, merah, anak mata membesar, dan urat darah
    jelas kelihatan.
  tindakan: Dapatkan rawatan kecemasan doktor haiwan segera.
  maklumatTambahan: Keadaan ini amat menyakitkan dan boleh membawa kepada buta kekal.
  puncaEN: Increased pressure within the eye due to fluid accumulation, which is
    usually inherited. Clear fluid that fills the space in the front part (Anterior
    Chamber).
  simptomEN: Eye appears cloudy/bluish, red, the pupil enlarges, and blood vessels
    are clearly visible.
  tindakanEN: Seek immediate emergency veterinary treatment.
  maklumatTambahanEN: This condition is extremely painful and can lead to permanent
    blindness.
